<br>
<i>"Summon someone who gives a damn"</i>
</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uyizznusnoonsunzziy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yizznusno Onsunzziy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#333333>(6/2/01 2:58:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Sebilis Tips?</span><hr size=1> I dunno about you guys, but i still have a hard time getting groups in here, even with coh.  One major problem of mine is i get in groups and they dont even realize that i have coh /sigh.  This is still a premium place to fight but i do constantly find myself fighting in karnors because of my impatience.  Only few suggestions i have now about this place is if you have coh, make it clear to your group =P and that you will also want to get your charasis key because alot of charasis pickup groups start here also.  All the other things i have to say have already been covered.  Also thanks for the info guys. <p>Yizznusno Onsunzziy<br>
