<br>
As far as KC goes I have a hard time getting a group there also....maybe I just have bad luck. hehe<br>
<br>
Keep your pet controlled...that is very important.  If it gets out of hand before they go for your group...do /q.  That way only one of you dies and rezzing one is better than all 6.<br>
