<br>
I started Seb at 53 and have been successful with groups ever since.  It takes time and patience to get a group.  Sebilis has a very long waiting line, and the zone is usually packed.  You can't exactly run to any camp either cuz that would be suicide.  Groups would often have to fight up, and since mages have the advantage with CoH, groups no longer have to fight up.<br>
<br>
If you want to be like in groups, MAKE SURE YOU CONTROL YOUR PET!!  Pet's are welcomed in Sebilis, just learn to control them.  Sometimes killing them is the best control.<br>
<br>
Nukers are always needed in a Sebilis group.  But nukers/mages are not priority positions.  Efficient groups have snarer, tanks, a cleric, and an enchanter.  A normal Seb group consists of 2-3 tanks (rangers/sk's always wanted for snare), an enchanter, a cleric, and the last slot preferably goes to a shaman but isn't necessary.  Nukers/mages can fill in that last slot just as long as there's already a snarer in the group.<br>
<br>
The thing about Mages getting hit by adds... Frogloks will attack almost anything in their way especially meditating casters or players who are sitting down.  It's just how Sebilis is.  As long as you have that cleric and enchanter, you'll be ok.<br>
<br>
Getting your Sebilis key is not a waste of time.  In fact, many high level guilds make it a requirement to get the key.  So save it, and use it when you want a good place to hunt. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=39.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=39.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=39.topic&index=11><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.threadControl?topicID=39.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=39.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=39.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowerannouncements">Administration<option value="themagicianstowergeneral">General<option value="themagicianstowerfrm32">Class Balance<option value="themagicianstowerfrm45">User Interface<option value="themagicianstowerspells">Spells<option value="themagicianstowerequipmentandquest